{"tid":1387698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望元朗嘅手足行過時留意返元朗廣場嘅連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:44:29.000Z","uid":209873,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57ab7c654c794296f2ffebbfbd72b335aa3b7070","tid":1387698,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"頭先發夢放工同屋企人食飯，路過元朗廣場連接輕鐵果條天橋時，見到連儂牆畀人撕曬落黎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EM7NkyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEM7NkyB.jpg&h=90357e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰時有個後生仔一個人喺度黐緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我同屋企人諗咗下，驚佢自己一個出事，就拿拿聲去隔嚟買膠紙幫手黐，甚至我再call個fd出嚟幫手<br />\n中途不斷有手足加入一齊幫手，甚至自發去買膠紙黎黐，更有個路過既嬸嬸喊住咁同一位黑衫手足講加油，成個場面真係超級感動，雖然唔知點解當場嘅反應係有啲想笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加感動嘅係我哋黐黐下有一堆人過來送水送餅送膠紙甚至送包書膠過黎&hellip;&hellip;真係無法形容嗰刻嘅心情，因為我平時都係送嘢畀學生嗰個，估唔到有朝一日會畀人送返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同我個fd都畢業咗幾年，出緊嚟做嘢，但我fd個樣好後生所以被送左唔少物資，佢都笑自己被誤認成需助養既學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為啲水同餅冇人拎，所以佢決定拎返屋企，等下次發夢再畀番D學生<br />\n<br />\n另外聽到大家支持嘅說話，感動之餘亦都受之有愧，因為我雖然一直都有發夢，但我唔敢企前線，所以希望大家可以支持返啲前線嘅學生，買多啲裝備佢哋，等佢哋唔好捱餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋都想呼籲一下元朗嘅手足， 得閒行過嘅話幫手留意下個連儂牆啦，好似冇乜人知嗰度有連儂牆咁，香港人加油！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8bFFy1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8bFFy1.jpg&h=4ccb93f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ac878c7ba0fe49ed4ddd14b235d1bb5fa6ff368","tid":1387698,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"8月5 全香港 齊罷工"},{"pid":"084b6399f4634a8a118cdf47aff815e2a6d29756","tid":1387698,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2aa91af74782d24e61f3020fe200364efa4e7688","tid":1387698,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"用鎖頭！<br />\n<br />\nE.g. 喺尖東海傍建立一個「連儂海傍」景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等大陸人打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApM28As.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApM28As.png&h=00b9d1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APRFVfu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPRFVfu.png&h=6c611bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkyXYkA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkyXYkA.png&h=7dfc92f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[永久連儂牆］點解唔用鎖頭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9a04fc6e605682cbd64ae8610cbe30dc43d8d99","tid":1387698,"uid":220515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a63389be2bc6a9c4aceef115eedde56404556375","tid":1387698,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}